BC Website Statistics extension DEBUG

Troubleshooting
===============

This document is a guide to debugging the BC Website Statistics extension

1. Settings
   --------

   Also make sure you have the proper settings in your
   Google Analytics account control panel.

2. Delay
   -----

   It regularly takes from 1 to 4 hours, on average, depending on day of week 
   and time of day for the google analytics report website to display stats 
   collected successfully.


